==English==

===Verb===
[[Category:English verbs]]
{{en-infl-reg-other-e|compet|e}}
# To contend [[emulously]]; 
# To seek or strive for the same thing, position, or reward for which another is striving. 
# To contend in rivalry, as for a prize or in business; as, tradesmen compete with one another.

